displayName: Jinami, the City of Martial Arts - Tavern

parameters:
Chef Meri: Sorry for moving without permission! I had no
choice but to come back due to work reasons.
Clea: This will be the promised honey.
\I[514] Delivered three bottles of premium honey.

Chef Meri: This is good honey...! But... *sniff sniff*... is
it a different kind...?

Chef Meri: I see, I understand now! I needed to mix a
different kind of honey!

Chef Meri: Thank you! With this, I can recreate the recipe
for happiness!

Chef Meri: I am a chef who has made numerous gourmets,
including the food connoisseur Koriba, marvel at my mother's
recipe!

Chef Meri: For my mother, cooking was always accompanied by
joy, so she called her recipes the recipes for happiness.
Thief Nora: Did you not learn the recipe?

Chef Meri: I received the recipe notes, but I can't catch up
unless I reproduce it with my own senses and taste.

Chef Meri: This time was lucky, but luck is also part of
skill! I'm really grateful, so this is a special reward.
Clea: Nora-san, did you have something to say?

Thief Nora: I-I'm fine...! Let's quickly return to our
journey... Now!
Chef Meri: Thanks to all of you, I'm really grateful!

Elderly man concerned about the empire: The empire affirms
violence too much. It should once again remember intellect
and moderation.

Bar Staff: There are a lot of customers here who touch me
inappropriately, even though the tips are good. It's really
troublesome...

Male Animal Trainer: Sniff sniff... sniff sniff... It still
smells beastly... I can't get rid of the smell of the
animals in the arena.

It seems that General Atu will be visiting the arena for an
inspection. I really want to see that hero's fighting style
up close at least once.

Information Broker: To think we can witness General Atu's
battle! I would love to see him fight seriously someday.

Researcher Makoto: The dream of making paintings move... If
the nobles won't provide financial support, then I'll do it
forcefully if I have to...

Researcher Makoto: That's ridiculous...! Why is this a
dream, with a beast-eared beauty like her...!?

Researcher Makoto: Please listen, Reverend. I was actually
planning to attack the nobles in order to raise funds...

Researcher Makoto: I'll stop doing foolish things and
instead, I'll show those nobles what I'm capable of with my
own achievements!

Researcher Makoto: I won't let anyone interfere with my
dream of bringing art to life. If you're interested, please
accept the piece that inspired my dream.

Researcher Makoto: The distance to my dream may be far...
but I'm starting to feel motivated.

Researcher Makoto: That's ridiculous...! Why is this a
dream, with a beast-eared beauty like her...!?

Innkeeper: Welcome to the arena of the drinkers! We have a
wide selection of strong and exciting alcoholic beverages.

Rude Man: This is our VIP seat, sorry but please find
another seat to drink or eat.
Do you call out to an assassin?

Assassin: The match is about to begin. Shall we go to work
too?

Assassin: Who are you guys? If you're prostitutes, wait
until we're done with our job.

Clea: The outcome should be decided fairly. I won't let you
interfere with Auto-san's final match.

Assassin: We're also here for work... As long as money is
involved, we'll give it our all.
